
systemctl status ssh	--> check ssh status
systemctl restart ssh	--> to restart
systemctl stop ssh	--> to stop
systemctl start ssh	--> to start
~/.ssh/known_hosts 	--> servers key lives on client
telnet ipaddress port	--> to check server port
nmap -p 22 ipaddress	-->another way to check if server   is open
iptables -vnL		--> check for firewall rules
ufw status verbose	--> check status of uncomplicated firewall
ufw enable		--> to enable
ufw disable		--> to disable
ufw app list		--> list applications profile
ufw allow ssh		--> allow incoming ssh connections

